---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const title = "Methodology";
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <h1 style="font-size: 34px; margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #111827;">Methodology</h1>

  <section style="color: #374151; max-width: 820px;">
    <p style="margin-top: 0;">
      We publish independent, short-biased research focused on corporate governance and disclosure risk.
      Our work is based on publicly available sources and reflects our opinions at the time of publication.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size: 16px; color: #111827; margin: 18px 0 8px;">Evidence standards</h2>
    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 18px;">
      <li>Primary sources whenever possible (filings, transcripts, court records, official disclosures).</li>
      <li>Clear citations and links to allow independent verification.</li>
      <li>Explicit separation between facts and interpretation.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size: 16px; color: #111827; margin: 18px 0 8px;">What we do</h2>
    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 18px;">
      <li>Analyze governance, incentives, disclosure quality, and business model sustainability.</li>
      <li>Document inconsistencies and material risks using verifiable evidence.</li>
      <li>Publish periodic reports with versioning and updates when warranted.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size: 16px; color: #111827; margin: 18px 0 8px;">What we do not do</h2>
    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 18px;">
      <li>No insider information or non-public material information.</li>
      <li>No personalized investment advice.</li>
      <li>No guarantees regarding accuracy, completeness, or outcomes.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size: 16px; color: #111827; margin: 18px 0 8px;">Corrections and updates</h2>
    <p style="margin: 0;">
      If we identify a material error, we will publish a corrected version and note the change.
      Readers may contact us via the Contact page with documented corrections.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>